1
00:00:00,500 --> 00:00:02,476
<Default><b>[stirring music]</b></Default>

2
00:00:02,500 --> 00:00:03,866
<Default><b>[GAELION] According
to the Water Dragon</b></Default>

3
00:00:03,890 --> 00:00:06,655
<Default><b>the barrier is controlled
from that lighthouse.</b></Default>

4
00:00:06,679 --> 00:00:09,196
<Default><b>If we're going to regroup
with those on the ship</b></Default>

5
00:00:09,220 --> 00:00:11,255
<Default><b>we'll have to disable
the barrier.</b></Default>

6
00:00:11,279 --> 00:00:13,956
<Default><b>I'd like to get them
in port as fast as we can.</b></Default>

7
00:00:13,980 --> 00:00:18,875
<Default><b>[sighs] Well, for the time
being, their stats seem OK.</b></Default>

8
00:00:18,899 --> 00:00:21,715
<Default><b>♪♪</b></Default>

9
00:00:21,739 --> 00:00:23,236
<Default><b>[ELHART] Feels like
no matter what we do</b></Default>

10
00:00:23,260 --> 00:00:24,776
<Default><b>we can't get any
closer to land.</b></Default>

11
00:00:24,800 --> 00:00:25,986
<Default><b>No kidding.</b></Default>

12
00:00:26,010 --> 00:00:28,456
<Default><b>I hope that the others
are OK out there.</b></Default>

13
00:00:28,480 --> 00:00:30,256
<Default><b>Master Naofumi.</b></Default>

14
00:00:30,280 --> 00:00:32,055
<Default><b>Raphy says they're fine</b></Default>

15
00:00:32,079 --> 00:00:35,235
<Default><b>Ugh! I don't have to worry
about Master Naofumi</b></Default>

16
00:00:35,259 --> 00:00:37,076
<Default><b>but that doesn't mean that
I still can't miss him!</b></Default>

17
00:00:37,100 --> 00:00:38,076
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

18
00:00:38,100 --> 00:00:39,077
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

19
00:00:39,101 --> 00:00:40,341
<Default><b>[shimmering]</b></Default>

20
00:00:42,439 --> 00:00:44,479
<Default><b>(distorted) Where
did Naofumi go?</b></Default>

21
00:00:47,619 --> 00:00:49,020
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

22
00:00:50,020 --> 00:00:51,655
<Default><b>[SADEENA]
Here we are!</b></Default>

23
00:00:51,679 --> 00:00:53,536
<Default><b>I don't know about this.</b></Default>

24
00:00:53,560 --> 00:00:54,875
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
I think it looks great.</b></Default>

25
00:00:54,899 --> 00:00:56,216
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

26
00:00:56,240 --> 00:00:58,455
<Default><b>Not to mention
it hides your face.</b></Default>

27
00:00:58,479 --> 00:01:00,716
<Default><b>- [chuckles awkwardly]
- Oh, and Raphtalia</b></Default>

28
00:01:00,740 --> 00:01:03,426
<Default><b>make sure that you don't
let your tail and ears show.</b></Default>

29
00:01:03,450 --> 00:01:05,346
<Default><b>Right. Oh.</b></Default>

30
00:01:05,370 --> 00:01:06,945
<Default><b>What is this?</b></Default>

31
00:01:06,969 --> 00:01:08,736
<Default><b>It's proof that
the Water Dragon</b></Default>

32
00:01:08,760 --> 00:01:10,665
<Default><b>has vowed to protect us.</b></Default>

33
00:01:10,689 --> 00:01:14,146
<Default><b>It's actually an object
of worship in this country.</b></Default>

34
00:01:14,170 --> 00:01:15,850
<Default><b>So it's something holy?</b></Default>

35
00:01:16,969 --> 00:01:19,695
<Default><b>Well, if we're all
done changing, let's go.</b></Default>

36
00:01:19,719 --> 00:01:21,025
<Default><b>[ALL] Mm.</b></Default>

37
00:01:21,049 --> 00:01:22,346
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] Our top
priority right</b></Default>

38
00:01:22,370 --> 00:01:24,760
<Default><b>now is to break
that barrier.</b></Default>

39
00:01:25,450 --> 00:01:28,426
<Default><b>[theme music]</b></Default>

40
00:01:28,450 --> 00:01:30,385
<Default><b>♪♪</b></Default>

41
00:01:30,409 --> 00:01:31,715
<Default><b>THE RISING OF
THE SHIELD HERO</b></Default>

42
00:01:31,739 --> 00:01:34,045
<Default><b>♪ Hey, no need
for hesitation ♪</b></Default>

43
00:01:34,069 --> 00:01:35,495
<Default><b>♪ Nothing standing
in our way ♪</b></Default>

44
00:01:35,519 --> 00:01:36,496
<Default><b>♪ Fight it right now ♪</b></Default>

45
00:01:36,520 --> 00:01:39,495
<Default><b>[singing in Japanese]</b></Default>

46
00:01:39,519 --> 00:01:46,519
<Default><b>♪♪</b></Default>

47
00:02:03,180 --> 00:02:04,766
<Default><b>♪ Don't let it go ♪</b></Default>

48
00:02:04,790 --> 00:02:06,025
<Default><b>♪ Don't let it go ♪</b></Default>

49
00:02:06,049 --> 00:02:09,365
<Default><b>♪ Don't tell me
nor anyone else ♪</b></Default>

50
00:02:09,389 --> 00:02:13,186
<Default><b>[singing in Japanese]</b></Default>

51
00:02:13,210 --> 00:02:16,286
<Default><b>♪ I will protect
your resolution ♪</b></Default>

52
00:02:16,310 --> 00:02:19,066
<Default><b>♪ No matter
what comes next ♪</b></Default>

53
00:02:19,090 --> 00:02:22,485
<Default><b>♪ 'Cause every time
again I stand my ground ♪</b></Default>

54
00:02:22,509 --> 00:02:24,665
<Default><b>♪ We'll never
lose and cry ♪</b></Default>

55
00:02:24,689 --> 00:02:28,336
<Default><b>♪ Now nobody can
stop us, no way ♪</b></Default>

56
00:02:28,360 --> 00:02:31,385
<Default><b>[singing in Japanese]</b></Default>

57
00:02:31,409 --> 00:02:37,506
<Default><b>♪♪</b></Default>

58
00:02:37,530 --> 00:02:42,075
<Default><b>♪ We protect
our resolution, yeah ♪</b></Default>

59
00:02:42,099 --> 00:02:44,466
<Default><b>♪ Hey, no need
for hesitation ♪</b></Default>

60
00:02:44,490 --> 00:02:46,385
<Default><b>♪ Nothing standing
in our way ♪</b></Default>

61
00:02:46,409 --> 00:02:48,096
<Default><b>♪ Fight it right now ♪</b></Default>

62
00:02:48,120 --> 00:02:51,026
<Default><b>♪ Hey, no need
for hesitation ♪</b></Default>

63
00:02:51,050 --> 00:02:53,990
<Default><b>[singing in Japanese]</b></Default>

64
00:02:55,479 --> 00:02:56,906
<Default><b>EPISODE 7:
"ARRIVING IN Q'TEN LO"</b></Default>

65
00:02:56,930 --> 00:02:59,115
<Default><b>[RAPHTALIA]
It really is beautiful here.</b></Default>

66
00:02:59,139 --> 00:03:02,536
<Default><b>[SADEENA] Come nightfall, the
Sakura Lumina begin to shine.</b></Default>

67
00:03:02,560 --> 00:03:06,276
<Default><b>They're also used as an energy
source for a lot of tools.</b></Default>

68
00:03:06,300 --> 00:03:07,635
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] Why don't
we take some home</b></Default>

69
00:03:07,659 --> 00:03:09,235
<Default><b>and grow them
in our village?</b></Default>

70
00:03:09,259 --> 00:03:11,276
<Default><b>[SADEENA] The thing is</b></Default>

71
00:03:11,300 --> 00:03:12,746
<Default><b>properly in
this country.</b></Default>

72
00:03:12,770 --> 00:03:13,890
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]</b></Default>

73
00:03:15,340 --> 00:03:17,235
<Default><b>I see.
Are they fishing out there?</b></Default>

74
00:03:17,259 --> 00:03:19,915
<Default><b>[SADEENA] Looks like
they're gathering seaweed.</b></Default>

75
00:03:19,939 --> 00:03:21,316
<Default><b>[GAELION]
It would be a lot easier</b></Default>

76
00:03:21,340 --> 00:03:22,836
<Default><b>if we could
just fly there.</b></Default>

77
00:03:22,860 --> 00:03:25,195
<Default><b>Until we get ourselves
shot out of the sky</b></Default>

78
00:03:25,219 --> 00:03:27,855
<Default><b>it's better to play it
safe and travel by land.</b></Default>

79
00:03:27,879 --> 00:03:29,806
<Default><b>♪♪</b></Default>

80
00:03:29,830 --> 00:03:33,716
<Default><b>[waves lapping gently]</b></Default>

81
00:03:33,740 --> 00:03:35,276
<Default><b>This place is bizarre.</b></Default>

82
00:03:35,300 --> 00:03:38,075
<Default><b>It's like Japanese
Raphtalia land.</b></Default>

83
00:03:38,099 --> 00:03:39,816
<Default><b>[RAPHTALIA]
Why all the decorations?</b></Default>

84
00:03:39,840 --> 00:03:42,436
<Default><b>[SADEENA] They're put there
in honor of the emperor's clan.</b></Default>

85
00:03:42,460 --> 00:03:45,476
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] So the emperor's
clan is loved by the people?</b></Default>

86
00:03:45,500 --> 00:03:46,836
<Default><b>I don't understand.</b></Default>

87
00:03:46,860 --> 00:03:48,195
<Default><b>If the emperor is adored</b></Default>

88
00:03:48,219 --> 00:03:49,596
<Default><b>then why did
my mom and dad</b></Default>

89
00:03:49,620 --> 00:03:51,566
<Default><b>have to leave Q'ten Lo?</b></Default>

90
00:03:51,590 --> 00:03:53,009
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

91
00:03:55,379 --> 00:03:56,776
<Default><b>[boy screaming]</b></Default>

92
00:03:56,800 --> 00:03:57,985
<Default><b>What's going on?</b></Default>

93
00:03:58,009 --> 00:03:59,240
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

94
00:04:00,240 --> 00:04:02,006
<Default><b>[whimpers]</b></Default>

95
00:04:02,030 --> 00:04:03,226
<Default><b>- Master Naofumi.
- On it.</b></Default>

96
00:04:03,250 --> 00:04:04,226
<Default><b>Hold on.</b></Default>

97
00:04:04,250 --> 00:04:05,227
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

98
00:04:05,251 --> 00:04:06,586
<Default><b>Do your thing, Gaelion.</b></Default>

99
00:04:06,610 --> 00:04:07,746
<Default><b>[chirrups]</b></Default>

100
00:04:07,770 --> 00:04:10,246
<Default><b>It's best you two
stay out of this.</b></Default>

101
00:04:10,270 --> 00:04:12,115
<Default><b>[yelling]</b></Default>

102
00:04:12,139 --> 00:04:15,015
<Default><b>[whimpers]</b></Default>

103
00:04:15,039 --> 00:04:16,719
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
Can you stand?</b></Default>

104
00:04:18,180 --> 00:04:20,430
<Default><b>[screams]</b></Default>

105
00:04:21,430 --> 00:04:22,846
<Default><b>Hey, wait!</b></Default>

106
00:04:22,870 --> 00:04:24,966
<Default><b>What was that about?</b></Default>

107
00:04:24,990 --> 00:04:26,365
<Default><b>How could you?</b></Default>

108
00:04:26,389 --> 00:04:27,886
<Default><b>Why do such a thing?</b></Default>

109
00:04:27,910 --> 00:04:30,346
<Default><b>Aren't you scared what
the magistrates will do?</b></Default>

110
00:04:30,370 --> 00:04:32,815
<Default><b>[footsteps approaching]</b></Default>

111
00:04:32,839 --> 00:04:34,286
<Default><b>[staffs clanging]</b></Default>

112
00:04:34,310 --> 00:04:36,766
<Default><b>[tense music]</b></Default>

113
00:04:36,790 --> 00:04:39,545
<Default><b>Am I correct to assume
that you killed that monster?</b></Default>

114
00:04:39,569 --> 00:04:41,706
<Default><b>Is it really so wrong
to save a helpless kid?</b></Default>

115
00:04:41,730 --> 00:04:44,245
<Default><b>I'm afraid you're mistaken
because all that happened here</b></Default>

116
00:04:44,269 --> 00:04:46,586
<Default><b>was one monster
devouring another one.</b></Default>

117
00:04:46,610 --> 00:04:47,646
<Default><b>[crowd gasping]</b></Default>

118
00:04:47,670 --> 00:04:49,365
<Default><b>Enough of the lies.</b></Default>

119
00:04:49,389 --> 00:04:51,305
<Default><b>Would you disobey
the emperor?</b></Default>

120
00:04:51,329 --> 00:04:52,805
<Default><b>Of course not.</b></Default>

121
00:04:52,829 --> 00:04:54,745
<Default><b>You seem like a smart
enough fellow</b></Default>

122
00:04:54,769 --> 00:04:57,735
<Default><b>which means you know what this
monster here is, don't you?</b></Default>

123
00:04:57,759 --> 00:04:59,435
<Default><b>A servant
of the Water Dragon?</b></Default>

124
00:04:59,459 --> 00:05:00,855
<Default><b>[gasping]</b></Default>

125
00:05:00,879 --> 00:05:02,359
<Default><b>Please forgive us!</b></Default>

126
00:05:04,100 --> 00:05:06,536
<Default><b>[PEASANT 1] Are they
messengers of the Water Dragon?</b></Default>

127
00:05:06,560 --> 00:05:08,536
<Default><b>[PEASANT 2] They must be
if they have that orb.</b></Default>

128
00:05:08,560 --> 00:05:10,406
<Default><b>I can't believe
it's gotten this bad.</b></Default>

129
00:05:10,430 --> 00:05:11,696
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

130
00:05:11,720 --> 00:05:13,146
<Default><b>[MURAMASA] Splendidly
done, young lady.</b></Default>

131
00:05:13,170 --> 00:05:14,147
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

132
00:05:14,171 --> 00:05:16,295
<Default><b>[crowd murmuring]</b></Default>

133
00:05:16,319 --> 00:05:18,875
<Default><b>[MURAMASA] While everyone else
was too scared to speak up</b></Default>

134
00:05:18,899 --> 00:05:21,935
<Default><b>you went and took action
to save that child's life.</b></Default>

135
00:05:21,959 --> 00:05:23,456
<Default><b>I think anyone
with a conscience</b></Default>

136
00:05:23,480 --> 00:05:25,055
<Default><b>would have done
the same thing.</b></Default>

137
00:05:25,079 --> 00:05:27,675
<Default><b>Your actions have
moved me, young lady.</b></Default>

138
00:05:27,699 --> 00:05:28,735
<Default><b>You've won my heart.</b></Default>

139
00:05:28,759 --> 00:05:29,736
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

140
00:05:29,760 --> 00:05:31,355
<Default><b>My name's Muramasa.</b></Default>

141
00:05:31,379 --> 00:05:34,136
<Default><b>It'd be my pleasure
to buy you a cup of tea.</b></Default>

142
00:05:34,160 --> 00:05:36,836
<Default><b>Sorry, but what is
it you think I did?</b></Default>

143
00:05:36,860 --> 00:05:39,636
<Default><b>That's very kind of you</b></Default>

144
00:05:39,660 --> 00:05:42,615
<Default><b>Oh, you're unbelievably
beautiful, too!</b></Default>

145
00:05:42,639 --> 00:05:45,855
<Default><b>Please, I beg of you</b></Default>

146
00:05:45,879 --> 00:05:47,795
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] He's going
after every girl he sees</b></Default>

147
00:05:47,819 --> 00:05:49,415
<Default><b>like Motoyasu.</b></Default>

148
00:05:49,439 --> 00:05:52,196
<Default><b>How very kind.
But I am taken.</b></Default>

149
00:05:52,220 --> 00:05:55,235
<Default><b>And like I said before, we
are in a bit of a hurry here.</b></Default>

150
00:05:55,259 --> 00:05:56,236
<Default><b>Oh, come on.</b></Default>

151
00:05:56,260 --> 00:05:57,865
<Default><b>Don't say that to me.</b></Default>

152
00:05:57,889 --> 00:05:58,866
<Default><b>[SADEENA]
Zweit Thunderbolt!</b></Default>

153
00:05:58,890 --> 00:06:00,680
<Default><b>[screaming]</b></Default>

154
00:06:01,680 --> 00:06:04,076
<Default><b>You've got some
kick to you, huh?</b></Default>

155
00:06:04,100 --> 00:06:05,456
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

156
00:06:05,480 --> 00:06:07,696
<Default><b>Looks like we've
attracted a crowd.</b></Default>

157
00:06:07,720 --> 00:06:09,115
<Default><b>We should get a move on.</b></Default>

158
00:06:09,139 --> 00:06:10,576
<Default><b>Yeah, no kidding.</b></Default>

159
00:06:10,600 --> 00:06:11,915
<Default><b>Let's hurry
up and leave.</b></Default>

160
00:06:11,939 --> 00:06:13,216
<Default><b>[SADEENA] Agreed.</b></Default>

161
00:06:13,240 --> 00:06:14,755
<Default><b>[RAPHTALIA]
What a strange old man.</b></Default>

162
00:06:14,779 --> 00:06:17,040
<Default><b>[crowd murmuring]</b></Default>

163
00:06:18,040 --> 00:06:21,696
<Default><b>[sighs] What the hell
was all that about?</b></Default>

164
00:06:21,720 --> 00:06:24,615
<Default><b>The magistrates were
upset because the emperor</b></Default>

165
00:06:24,639 --> 00:06:28,355
<Default><b>forbids killing all living
things, even big monsters.</b></Default>

166
00:06:28,379 --> 00:06:29,735
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

167
00:06:29,759 --> 00:06:32,735
<Default><b>Sounds like the beliefs
of one of the old shoguns.</b></Default>

168
00:06:32,759 --> 00:06:35,295
<Default><b>Do you mind explaining
what a shogun is?</b></Default>

169
00:06:35,319 --> 00:06:37,786
<Default><b>In any case, I'm
glad Gaelion was here.</b></Default>

170
00:06:37,810 --> 00:06:38,896
<Default><b>[chirrups]</b></Default>

171
00:06:38,920 --> 00:06:40,175
<Default><b>So what you're
saying is they can't</b></Default>

172
00:06:40,199 --> 00:06:42,266
<Default><b>punish a monster for the
killing of another</b></Default>

173
00:06:42,290 --> 00:06:43,656
<Default><b>monster, huh?</b></Default>

174
00:06:43,680 --> 00:06:45,855
<Default><b>Well, if the monster's
owner made them do it</b></Default>

175
00:06:45,879 --> 00:06:47,776
<Default><b>I'm sure the owner
would be punished.</b></Default>

176
00:06:47,800 --> 00:06:49,696
<Default><b>But they can't do
anything if it's</b></Default>

177
00:06:49,720 --> 00:06:51,396
<Default><b>a servant of the
Water Dragon.</b></Default>

178
00:06:51,420 --> 00:06:53,295
<Default><b>It sounds like we made
the best use of what</b></Default>

179
00:06:53,319 --> 00:06:54,935
<Default><b>the Water
Dragon gave us.</b></Default>

180
00:06:54,959 --> 00:06:55,959
<Default><b>Hmm.</b></Default>

181
00:06:57,290 --> 00:07:01,206
<Default><b>Which means it's illegal
to even fish in this country.</b></Default>

182
00:07:01,230 --> 00:07:03,065
<Default><b>That is exactly correct.</b></Default>

183
00:07:03,089 --> 00:07:05,776
<Default><b>That's why those fishermen
were gathering seaweed.</b></Default>

184
00:07:05,800 --> 00:07:07,226
<Default><b>[FISHERMAN]
Please don't!</b></Default>

185
00:07:07,250 --> 00:07:09,065
<Default><b>If you take that</b></Default>

186
00:07:09,089 --> 00:07:11,065
<Default><b>Those who don't
pay their taxes</b></Default>

187
00:07:11,089 --> 00:07:12,966
<Default><b>are no different
than mere traitors!</b></Default>

188
00:07:12,990 --> 00:07:16,565
<Default><b>[grunts] But, sir</b></Default>

189
00:07:16,589 --> 00:07:19,985
<Default><b>Do you mean to say that you
would disobey the emperor?</b></Default>

190
00:07:20,009 --> 00:07:21,485
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

191
00:07:21,509 --> 00:07:24,509
<Default><b>[somber music]</b></Default>

192
00:07:25,930 --> 00:07:27,090
<Default><b>Raphtalia.</b></Default>

193
00:07:28,689 --> 00:07:31,295
<Default><b>We might just be able
to use this to our advantage.</b></Default>

194
00:07:31,319 --> 00:07:32,636
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

195
00:07:32,660 --> 00:07:34,706
<Default><b>I can't imagine that
too many of the citizens</b></Default>

196
00:07:34,730 --> 00:07:37,036
<Default><b>are very happy
about this law.</b></Default>

197
00:07:37,060 --> 00:07:38,037
<Default><b>Hmm.</b></Default>

198
00:07:38,061 --> 00:07:39,425
<Default><b>Hmm, what's wrong?</b></Default>

199
00:07:39,449 --> 00:07:40,985
<Default><b>We're not alone.</b></Default>

200
00:07:41,009 --> 00:07:45,586
<Default><b>♪♪</b></Default>

201
00:07:45,610 --> 00:07:46,906
<Default><b>A magistrate?</b></Default>

202
00:07:46,930 --> 00:07:48,665
<Default><b>I couldn't say.</b></Default>

203
00:07:48,689 --> 00:07:50,545
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
We'll use invisibility magic.</b></Default>

204
00:07:50,569 --> 00:07:51,969
<Default><b>[SADEENA] Right.</b></Default>

205
00:07:52,800 --> 00:07:54,675
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

206
00:07:54,699 --> 00:07:57,560
<Default><b>[mysterious music]</b></Default>

207
00:08:00,769 --> 00:08:02,206
<Default><b>Forgive me!</b></Default>

208
00:08:02,230 --> 00:08:05,076
<Default><b>Wherever you are, please
know I am not your enemy.</b></Default>

209
00:08:05,100 --> 00:08:06,555
<Default><b>The sea people
have shared with me</b></Default>

210
00:08:06,579 --> 00:08:08,755
<Default><b>the words of the
Water Dragon.</b></Default>

211
00:08:08,779 --> 00:08:12,755
<Default><b>I've sought you out to welcome
you here with open arms.</b></Default>

212
00:08:12,779 --> 00:08:15,795
<Default><b>If you are still here</b></Default>

213
00:08:15,819 --> 00:08:17,795
<Default><b>- [NAOFUMI] Raphtalia.
- Huh?</b></Default>

214
00:08:17,819 --> 00:08:19,435
<Default><b>[SADEENA] He must
be telling the truth.</b></Default>

215
00:08:19,459 --> 00:08:21,375
<Default><b>The timing would be
far too convenient.</b></Default>

216
00:08:21,399 --> 00:08:22,376
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] Hey.</b></Default>

217
00:08:22,400 --> 00:08:23,516
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

218
00:08:23,540 --> 00:08:25,500
<Default><b>Get off your knees
and face us.</b></Default>

219
00:08:27,060 --> 00:08:28,036
<Default><b>Mm.</b></Default>

220
00:08:28,060 --> 00:08:29,037
<Default><b>So, um...</b></Default>

221
00:08:29,061 --> 00:08:30,336
<Default><b>You have our attention.</b></Default>

222
00:08:30,360 --> 00:08:32,696
<Default><b>So let's hear who you
are and what you want.</b></Default>

223
00:08:32,720 --> 00:08:34,196
<Default><b>My name is Luminus.</b></Default>

224
00:08:34,220 --> 00:08:36,296
<Default><b>My father is Raluva</b></Default>

225
00:08:36,320 --> 00:08:37,916
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
Just get to the point!</b></Default>

226
00:08:37,940 --> 00:08:39,235
<Default><b>But, sir...</b></Default>

227
00:08:39,259 --> 00:08:40,495
<Default><b>You can relax.</b></Default>

228
00:08:40,519 --> 00:08:42,316
<Default><b>There's no need for all
the formalities.</b></Default>

229
00:08:42,340 --> 00:08:44,395
<Default><b>Then so be it.</b></Default>

230
00:08:44,419 --> 00:08:46,436
<Default><b>In that case, the people
here in this city</b></Default>

231
00:08:46,460 --> 00:08:48,476
<Default><b>are in desperate
need of your help.</b></Default>

232
00:08:48,500 --> 00:08:50,436
<Default><b>But why seek
us for help?</b></Default>

233
00:08:50,460 --> 00:08:51,775
<Default><b>Take a look around.</b></Default>

234
00:08:51,799 --> 00:08:53,166
<Default><b>It doesn't take
much to see</b></Default>

235
00:08:53,190 --> 00:08:54,806
<Default><b>what's been
happening here.</b></Default>

236
00:08:54,830 --> 00:08:57,285
<Default><b>You mean the "no killing
living things" law?</b></Default>

237
00:08:57,309 --> 00:08:59,326
<Default><b>And the taxes
are horrible.</b></Default>

238
00:08:59,350 --> 00:09:01,846
<Default><b>Some of the people
are even starving.</b></Default>

239
00:09:01,870 --> 00:09:03,285
<Default><b>This can't continue.</b></Default>

240
00:09:03,309 --> 00:09:06,046
<Default><b>This tyranny must
come to an end!</b></Default>

241
00:09:06,070 --> 00:09:08,245
<Default><b>So the people aren't
happy with the emperor.</b></Default>

242
00:09:08,269 --> 00:09:09,365
<Default><b>Is that it?</b></Default>

243
00:09:09,389 --> 00:09:10,605
<Default><b>And there's more.</b></Default>

244
00:09:10,629 --> 00:09:12,966
<Default><b>Allow me to explain
back at the mansion.</b></Default>

245
00:09:12,990 --> 00:09:15,605
<Default><b>Would you be willing
to come with us right now?</b></Default>

246
00:09:15,629 --> 00:09:18,025
<Default><b>I suppose it couldn't
hurt to hear him out.</b></Default>

247
00:09:18,049 --> 00:09:19,686
<Default><b>I don't see why not.</b></Default>

248
00:09:19,710 --> 00:09:22,456
<Default><b>Don't get any ideas about
setting us up for a trap.</b></Default>

249
00:09:22,480 --> 00:09:24,726
<Default><b>Look, I would
never do that!</b></Default>

250
00:09:24,750 --> 00:09:26,265
<Default><b>If I somehow
offended you</b></Default>

251
00:09:26,289 --> 00:09:28,289
<Default><b>I'll happily strike
myself down.</b></Default>

252
00:09:33,350 --> 00:09:34,625
<Default><b>My name is Raluva.</b></Default>

253
00:09:34,649 --> 00:09:36,365
<Default><b>I'm the city mayor.</b></Default>

254
00:09:36,389 --> 00:09:40,005
<Default><b>If it's not too
much trouble</b></Default>

255
00:09:40,029 --> 00:09:42,495
<Default><b>of looking
upon your face?</b></Default>

256
00:09:42,519 --> 00:09:44,476
<Default><b>[men gasp]</b></Default>

257
00:09:44,500 --> 00:09:47,985
<Default><b>Ah. I see now you resemble
that of your father.</b></Default>

258
00:09:48,009 --> 00:09:51,046
<Default><b>So wait. Then does that
mean you knew him?</b></Default>

259
00:09:51,070 --> 00:09:53,395
<Default><b>Your father was
very kind to me.</b></Default>

260
00:09:53,419 --> 00:09:55,596
<Default><b>I'm starting
to remember things now.</b></Default>

261
00:09:55,620 --> 00:09:57,476
<Default><b>You were close with
him, weren't you?</b></Default>

262
00:09:57,500 --> 00:09:59,755
<Default><b>You're the former miko
of the Water Dragon.</b></Default>

263
00:09:59,779 --> 00:10:01,265
<Default><b>It's been a while.</b></Default>

264
00:10:01,289 --> 00:10:04,416
<Default><b>My name is
Naofumi Iwatani</b></Default>

265
00:10:04,440 --> 00:10:06,176
<Default><b>I'm familiar with you.</b></Default>

266
00:10:06,200 --> 00:10:08,936
<Default><b>Though we haven't met</b></Default>

267
00:10:08,960 --> 00:10:12,296
<Default><b>You have my eternal thanks
for keeping Raphtalia safe.</b></Default>

268
00:10:12,320 --> 00:10:14,316
<Default><b>I thought this
place was cut off</b></Default>

269
00:10:14,340 --> 00:10:16,155
<Default><b>but you know about
the outside world.</b></Default>

270
00:10:16,179 --> 00:10:19,416
<Default><b>Why, yes. After all</b></Default>

271
00:10:19,440 --> 00:10:20,775
<Default><b>That makes sense.</b></Default>

272
00:10:20,799 --> 00:10:22,596
<Default><b>Well, let's cut
the chit-chat.</b></Default>

273
00:10:22,620 --> 00:10:24,836
<Default><b>What exactly do you
mean you want our help?</b></Default>

274
00:10:24,860 --> 00:10:26,456
<Default><b>Mm.</b></Default>

275
00:10:26,480 --> 00:10:28,576
<Default><b>What we want</b></Default>

276
00:10:28,600 --> 00:10:30,255
<Default><b>for Raphtalia
to take the throne</b></Default>

277
00:10:30,279 --> 00:10:32,076
<Default><b>and put an end
to this government.</b></Default>

278
00:10:32,100 --> 00:10:33,155
<Default><b>Take the throne?</b></Default>

279
00:10:33,179 --> 00:10:35,096
<Default><b>Do... do you
really mean...</b></Default>

280
00:10:35,120 --> 00:10:37,416
<Default><b>We came to this country
to work things out</b></Default>

281
00:10:37,440 --> 00:10:39,135
<Default><b>with whoever it
was that's sending</b></Default>

282
00:10:39,159 --> 00:10:41,176
<Default><b>assassins
after Raphtalia.</b></Default>

283
00:10:41,200 --> 00:10:44,495
<Default><b>Once things have been
settled, we'll be leaving.</b></Default>

284
00:10:44,519 --> 00:10:46,676
<Default><b>I am aware
of your intentions.</b></Default>

285
00:10:46,700 --> 00:10:48,316
<Default><b>And you're not
opposed to that?</b></Default>

286
00:10:48,340 --> 00:10:50,416
<Default><b>If she would become
a puppet emperor</b></Default>

287
00:10:50,440 --> 00:10:52,635
<Default><b>she would be no different
than the current one</b></Default>

288
00:10:52,659 --> 00:10:55,056
<Default><b>and all the people would
still be suffering.</b></Default>

289
00:10:55,080 --> 00:10:58,196
<Default><b>For the sake
of the world</b></Default>

290
00:10:58,220 --> 00:11:00,495
<Default><b>They should be
a driving force of good.</b></Default>

291
00:11:00,519 --> 00:11:04,155
<Default><b>Even Raphtalia's father
felt the same way.</b></Default>

292
00:11:04,179 --> 00:11:07,485
<Default><b>[gasps] Is that
the reason he left?</b></Default>

293
00:11:07,509 --> 00:11:10,235
<Default><b>I had no idea it had
to do with all of this.</b></Default>

294
00:11:10,259 --> 00:11:12,296
<Default><b>That isn't the
only reason.</b></Default>

295
00:11:12,320 --> 00:11:15,375
<Default><b>In that time, there was an ugly
fight over who was to be</b></Default>

296
00:11:15,399 --> 00:11:17,476
<Default><b>crowned the
next emperor.</b></Default>

297
00:11:17,500 --> 00:11:19,885
<Default><b>[clattering,
woman screaming]</b></Default>

298
00:11:19,909 --> 00:11:22,789
<Default><b>[woman sobbing]</b></Default>

299
00:11:26,639 --> 00:11:28,816
<Default><b>If he stayed
in this country, it</b></Default>

300
00:11:28,840 --> 00:11:31,735
<Default><b>would have meant accepting
a most horrible death.</b></Default>

301
00:11:31,759 --> 00:11:33,535
<Default><b>So that's it.</b></Default>

302
00:11:33,559 --> 00:11:36,936
<Default><b>We've waited up until
this very moment, the moment</b></Default>

303
00:11:36,960 --> 00:11:40,535
<Default><b>the true emperor finally
returned and put an end, once</b></Default>

304
00:11:40,559 --> 00:11:43,655
<Default><b>and for all, to the tyranny
we've been facing.</b></Default>

305
00:11:43,679 --> 00:11:46,135
<Default><b>So what is your plan
going forward?</b></Default>

306
00:11:46,159 --> 00:11:48,296
<Default><b>First, eliminate
the magistrates</b></Default>

307
00:11:48,320 --> 00:11:49,696
<Default><b>guarding the lighthouse.</b></Default>

308
00:11:49,720 --> 00:11:52,265
<Default><b>That will likely
start a revolution.</b></Default>

309
00:11:52,289 --> 00:11:55,166
<Default><b>If I'm not mistaken</b></Default>

310
00:11:55,190 --> 00:11:56,926
<Default><b>Do you have all
your troops ready?</b></Default>

311
00:11:56,950 --> 00:12:00,586
<Default><b>I have my clan, also
the people of the town</b></Default>

312
00:12:00,610 --> 00:12:02,125
<Default><b>all of which are
ready to rise up.</b></Default>

313
00:12:02,149 --> 00:12:03,149
<Default><b>Good.</b></Default>

314
00:12:06,570 --> 00:12:08,265
<Default><b>Master Naofumi.</b></Default>

315
00:12:08,289 --> 00:12:10,635
<Default><b>Raphtalia, get
the miko outfit.</b></Default>

316
00:12:10,659 --> 00:12:11,745
<Default><b>[men gasping]</b></Default>

317
00:12:11,769 --> 00:12:13,226
<Default><b>Are you positive?</b></Default>

318
00:12:13,250 --> 00:12:15,290
<Default><b>If I wear it, then
that means...</b></Default>

319
00:12:16,889 --> 00:12:18,209
<Default><b>[RALUVA] Here.</b></Default>

320
00:12:19,210 --> 00:12:22,005
<Default><b>The second I wear
this, we'll be attacked.</b></Default>

321
00:12:22,029 --> 00:12:24,365
<Default><b>Well, they're going to be
coming after us anyway.</b></Default>

322
00:12:24,389 --> 00:12:26,645
<Default><b>And it's always better
to have more allies.</b></Default>

323
00:12:26,669 --> 00:12:28,226
<Default><b>I understand, but...</b></Default>

324
00:12:28,250 --> 00:12:29,946
<Default><b>I want to get
that barrier down</b></Default>

325
00:12:29,970 --> 00:12:33,226
<Default><b>fast so we can finally regroup
with those on the ship.</b></Default>

326
00:12:33,250 --> 00:12:35,865
<Default><b>And besides, just look.</b></Default>

327
00:12:35,889 --> 00:12:38,226
<Default><b>Judging from their eyes</b></Default>

328
00:12:38,250 --> 00:12:40,960
<Default><b>a long time
for a sign of hope to appear.</b></Default>

329
00:12:42,850 --> 00:12:44,570
<Default><b>I'll help you put it on.</b></Default>

330
00:12:49,899 --> 00:12:51,179
<Default><b>[men gasping]</b></Default>

331
00:12:52,169 --> 00:12:53,495
<Default><b>[men grunting in unison]</b></Default>

332
00:12:53,519 --> 00:12:55,416
<Default><b>Oh, don't do that.</b></Default>

333
00:12:55,440 --> 00:12:57,690
<Default><b>WATER DRAGON'S
MIKO DRESS - CRUDE</b></Default>

334
00:12:58,659 --> 00:13:02,196
<Default><b>Please, Emperor, we ask
that you guide us to victory.</b></Default>

335
00:13:02,220 --> 00:13:03,456
<Default><b>Just say the word.</b></Default>

336
00:13:03,480 --> 00:13:05,840
<Default><b>We're ready to follow
your every command.</b></Default>

337
00:13:06,860 --> 00:13:09,885
<Default><b>Proud citizens
of Q'ten Lo, hear me now!</b></Default>

338
00:13:09,909 --> 00:13:11,155
<Default><b>[MEN] Huh?</b></Default>

339
00:13:11,179 --> 00:13:13,716
<Default><b>The true emperor
has returned to you!</b></Default>

340
00:13:13,740 --> 00:13:16,895
<Default><b>Now is your chance to finally
put an end to this government.</b></Default>

341
00:13:16,919 --> 00:13:20,436
<Default><b>Offer up your hearts, and the
true emperor will lead you.</b></Default>

342
00:13:20,460 --> 00:13:21,615
<Default><b>For Q'ten Lo!</b></Default>

343
00:13:21,639 --> 00:13:22,995
<Default><b>For the people!</b></Default>

344
00:13:23,019 --> 00:13:25,216
<Default><b>Come with us if you
want to fight back!</b></Default>

345
00:13:25,240 --> 00:13:26,696
<Default><b>[men yelling in unison]</b></Default>

346
00:13:26,720 --> 00:13:29,485
<Default><b>[soft music]</b></Default>

347
00:13:29,509 --> 00:13:31,015
<Default><b>♪♪</b></Default>

348
00:13:31,039 --> 00:13:34,816
<Default><b>Master Naofumi, you imitated
Atla to get them fired up.</b></Default>

349
00:13:34,840 --> 00:13:36,596
<Default><b>And it worked
brilliantly.</b></Default>

350
00:13:36,620 --> 00:13:39,135
<Default><b>I'm getting excited
just thinking about it!</b></Default>

351
00:13:39,159 --> 00:13:41,076
<Default><b>It's better if we
take the lead.</b></Default>

352
00:13:41,100 --> 00:13:43,615
<Default><b>I don't want any
unnecessary casualties.</b></Default>

353
00:13:43,639 --> 00:13:46,596
<Default><b>[sighs] I understand.</b></Default>

354
00:13:46,620 --> 00:13:50,056
<Default><b>We can't avoid this</b></Default>

355
00:13:50,080 --> 00:13:52,865
<Default><b>[tense music]</b></Default>

356
00:13:52,889 --> 00:13:55,686
<Default><b>[footsteps marching]</b></Default>

357
00:13:55,710 --> 00:13:56,985
<Default><b>Halt right there!</b></Default>

358
00:13:57,009 --> 00:13:58,765
<Default><b>You approach holy
ground belonging</b></Default>

359
00:13:58,789 --> 00:14:00,306
<Default><b>to the emperor himself.</b></Default>

360
00:14:00,330 --> 00:14:03,446
<Default><b>Go and tell your leader
that the true emperor requests</b></Default>

361
00:14:03,470 --> 00:14:04,806
<Default><b>an audience with them.</b></Default>

362
00:14:04,830 --> 00:14:07,365
<Default><b>You must be the false
emperor and the holders</b></Default>

363
00:14:07,389 --> 00:14:09,645
<Default><b>of the evil spirit
implements!</b></Default>

364
00:14:09,669 --> 00:14:11,666
<Default><b>We don't negotiate
with traitors!</b></Default>

365
00:14:11,690 --> 00:14:13,306
<Default><b>Eliminate them!</b></Default>

366
00:14:13,330 --> 00:14:15,086
<Default><b>[dramatic music]</b></Default>

367
00:14:15,110 --> 00:14:17,466
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
Can't say I didn't expect this.</b></Default>

368
00:14:17,490 --> 00:14:18,467
<Default><b>Attack!</b></Default>

369
00:14:18,491 --> 00:14:21,765
<Default><b>[yelling]</b></Default>

370
00:14:21,789 --> 00:14:23,046
<Default><b>[yells]</b></Default>

371
00:14:23,070 --> 00:14:24,765
<Default><b>Meteor shield!</b></Default>

372
00:14:24,789 --> 00:14:28,405
<Default><b>If you think
that'll work</b></Default>

373
00:14:28,429 --> 00:14:30,735
<Default><b>[sword clanging</b></Default>

374
00:14:30,759 --> 00:14:32,265
<Default><b>Gah! Damn it!</b></Default>

375
00:14:32,289 --> 00:14:33,706
<Default><b>The bastard blinded me!</b></Default>

376
00:14:33,730 --> 00:14:36,145
<Default><b>You weren't the only ones
getting ready for this!</b></Default>

377
00:14:36,169 --> 00:14:38,446
<Default><b>All Zweit Aura!</b></Default>

378
00:14:38,470 --> 00:14:39,447
<Default><b>Raphtalia.</b></Default>

379
00:14:39,471 --> 00:14:40,466
<Default><b>Right!</b></Default>

380
00:14:40,490 --> 00:14:41,990
<Default><b>[blasting]</b></Default>

381
00:14:42,990 --> 00:14:44,070
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

382
00:14:44,990 --> 00:14:46,946
<Default><b>Follow the true
emperor into battle!</b></Default>

383
00:14:46,970 --> 00:14:48,385
<Default><b>Yes, Father!</b></Default>

384
00:14:48,409 --> 00:14:50,796
<Default><b>[men yelling]</b></Default>

385
00:14:50,820 --> 00:14:52,230
<Default><b>[chirrups]</b></Default>

386
00:14:53,230 --> 00:14:54,265
<Default><b>Now's our chance!</b></Default>

387
00:14:54,289 --> 00:14:55,266
<Default><b>Let's go!</b></Default>

388
00:14:55,290 --> 00:14:56,466
<Default><b>Right!</b></Default>

389
00:14:56,490 --> 00:15:01,005
<Default><b>♪♪</b></Default>

390
00:15:01,029 --> 00:15:02,645
<Default><b>This is the lighthouse.</b></Default>

391
00:15:02,669 --> 00:15:04,966
<Default><b>[RAPHTALIA]
If we can put out that fire...</b></Default>

392
00:15:04,990 --> 00:15:06,446
<Default><b>[staff clanging]</b></Default>

393
00:15:06,470 --> 00:15:08,206
<Default><b>What are you lot doing?</b></Default>

394
00:15:08,230 --> 00:15:10,166
<Default><b>Stop dawdling
around like fools</b></Default>

395
00:15:10,190 --> 00:15:12,765
<Default><b>and strike down
the false emperor!</b></Default>

396
00:15:12,789 --> 00:15:14,566
<Default><b>This guy must
be the boss.</b></Default>

397
00:15:14,590 --> 00:15:16,030
<Default><b>It would seem so.</b></Default>

398
00:15:17,259 --> 00:15:19,645
<Default><b>[BEARGA] Coward who
claims to be the emperor</b></Default>

399
00:15:19,669 --> 00:15:21,995
<Default><b>you shall soon feel
the mighty wrath of I</b></Default>

400
00:15:22,019 --> 00:15:25,155
<Default><b>Bearga, he who has been blessed
by the one true emperor!</b></Default>

401
00:15:25,179 --> 00:15:26,579
<Default><b>[staff clanging]</b></Default>

402
00:15:29,570 --> 00:15:31,566
<Default><b>- What the hell?
- What happened?</b></Default>

403
00:15:31,590 --> 00:15:34,850
<Default><b>The protection Naofumi gave
us, he somehow disabled it.</b></Default>

404
00:15:36,549 --> 00:15:37,765
<Default><b>That stone!</b></Default>

405
00:15:37,789 --> 00:15:39,605
